title: MONDAY - Week 11 recap 2020
itunes:title: MONDAY - Week 11 recap 2020
description:
Some great matchups in Week 11...The Chiefs (0:13) show why they are the premiere team in the AFC as they took on the Raiders. The Ravens (1:02) drop a tough one to the Titans as they've now lost 4 games on the season. We'll hear from Lamar Jackson (1:54) on Baltimore's mindset. Meanwhile, it was a battle of two legendary QB's in Indianapolis (2:50) as Philip Rivers outlasting Aaron Rodgers and the Packers. Plus, Taysom Hill (3:38) shines in his first NFL start
